#           Arg.Int / Float, Arg.Set_string ref / Set_int ref,
#           Arg.Tuple [specs...] (multi-arg flag), Arg.Symbol
#           [vals] fn (enum), Arg.Rest fn (catch-all
#           remaining args).  Plus `Arg.align` for alignment of
#           help text columns and `Arg.usage` for printing
#           usage.  Used by EVERY OCaml CLI tool — the de-facto
#           OCaml argv-parsing standard.)
